release_note: New Activities: Ring in the new year with activities focused on letting go of the negative setting goals and finding gratitude Entry Naming: Your drawings are unique your journal is personal and now your entry name can be customized too! Browse by Intention: The Discover tab is now browsable by a specific intention i.e Navigate Anxiety. Monthly Subscription Option: You asked we listened. Subscribe to Scribble Journey month by month. Minor bug fixes and improvements

you can now view all activity descriptions before subscribing! more guidance if anything goes wrong with subscribing image sizes improved for more uniformity fixed bug where updating photos may not update

new transitions between steps in completing an activity that fit the mood finalizing activities available at launch even a sneak peak at future cards new groups in the Featured tab helpful images when completing an activity will stack on one another backend improvements for subscriptions
